y:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">编辑：英智</span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;margin:10px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;max-width:100%;word-break:break-all !important;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">【新智元导读】</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从代码补全到全流程开发，AI正以前所未有的速度改变软件开发的规则。本文深入解析了L1到L5五个等级的AI编程工具，展望了AI编程的全面自动化</span><span style=\"font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;\">。</span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;\">AI恰似一把神奇的钥匙，悄然</span><span style=\"font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;\">开启了编程领域的全新大门。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从代码补全到项目级自动化，AI的角色从「助手」转变为「工程师」，甚至是「开发团队」，极大地改变了软件开发的传统格局。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">借鉴自动驾驶的术语，AI编程工具可以划分为L1到L5五个等级。接下来将详细介绍。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"308\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1051\" data-imgfileid=\"505076551\" data-ratio=\"0.5472222222222223\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/24455983-152f-4c5d-0b30-14f42b16be00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1921\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/24455983-152f-4c5d-0b30-14f42b16be00/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"330\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1119\" data-imgfileid=\"505076553\" data-ratio=\"0.5879629629629629\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/835b90d6-351c-41b4-6a1b-c29cca974300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1904\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/835b90d6-351c-41b4-6a1b-c29cca974300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">2025年1月AI编程领域可视化图</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">L1：代码补全</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从基础功能层面来看，以GitHub Copilot为代表的L1级工具，主要聚焦于代码补全。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">开发者常常会面临一些重复、繁琐的代码输入，这类工具极具实用价值，通过智能建议与代码补全功能，能极大地简化编码流程。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在现代开发环境中，L1级的代码补全工具已经极为普遍，为更先进的AI编程工具奠定了坚实的基础。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"361\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"880\" data-imgfileid=\"505076552\" data-ratio=\"0.6416666666666667\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a3ad31c2-3144-48dd-1fba-ac64ced1a700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1371\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a3ad31c2-3144-48dd-1fba-ac64ced1a700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">GitHub Copilot擅长代码补全</span></p>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"373\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"601\" data-imgfileid=\"505076550\" data-ratio=\"0.6633554083885209\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c8ec8c8f-2c8d-46d2-bb66-e6ee56620d00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"906\" data-width=\"906\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c8ec8c8f-2c8d-46d2-bb66-e6ee56620d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">代码补全（L1）产品</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">L2：任务自动化</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">L2级别的工具专注于任务级自动化，LLM如ChatGPT便属于这一范畴。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这类工具擅长处理各种开发任务，能够依据描述性提示来开发新功能、修复漏洞以及重构代码。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"418\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1005\" data-imgfileid=\"505076554\" data-ratio=\"0.7435185185185185\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/24c10e40-b1df-4b77-ba43-25aa939f5e00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1352\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/24c10e40-b1df-4b77-ba43-25aa939f5e00/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，在实际使用过程中，使用LLM进行编码任务也面临着一些挑战。例如，它需要精心设计的提示以及相关源代码上下文，才能生成高质量的代码，而手动创建提示既耗时又繁琐。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了解决这一问题，一些工作流自动化工具应运而生，如命令行工具aider和桌面应用程序16x Prompt，它们能够简化提示生成过程，帮助开发者从LLM中获取高质量代码。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"367\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1180\" data-imgfileid=\"505076555\" data-ratio=\"0.6537037037037037\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d6f6d144-9d30-46e8-904f-f77e33b72100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1804\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d6f6d144-9d30-46e8-904f-f77e33b72100/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，Cursor、Continue和PearAI等集成开发环境（IDE）及其扩展，能够将LLM无缝集成到开发环境中，为开发者提供更友好的交互界面，让他们在开发过程中能够更便捷地与LLM互动，实现编程任务的自动化。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"372\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"605\" data-imgfileid=\"505076556\" data-ratio=\"0.6612021857923497\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/848f4a9f-abb7-4b31-bf75-4e2dd23ff400/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"915\" data-width=\"915\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/848f4a9f-abb7-4b31-bf75-4e2dd23ff400/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"460\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"795\" data-imgfileid=\"505076558\" data-ratio=\"0.8179012345679012\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7a82960d-ead3-4b9b-b815-32f4ed334700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"972\" data-width=\"972\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7a82960d-ead3-4b9b-b815-32f4ed334700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">任务级自动化（L2）产品</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">L3：项目自动化</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">L3代表着项目级自动化的早期阶段，像Codegen、Sweep 和 Pythagora这样的工具，具备分析项目需求并生成相关拉取请求的能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"290\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1021\" data-imgfileid=\"505076559\" data-ratio=\"0.5157407407407407\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7b8ba1eb-c66f-4607-6970-2238bd45c600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1981\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7b8ba1eb-c66f-4607-6970-2238bd45c600/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">L3级工具的一个关键特性在于，它们能够通过与项目管理工具（如Jira）和源代码平台（如GitHub）集成，实现软件开发多个步骤的自动化，包括需求收集、代码生成、拉取请求创建和部署。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，目前这些系统尚处于初级阶段，仅能管理较为简单的编码项目，并生成基本的代码片段。在实际应用中，还需要人工进行干预，以确保代码的质量和相关性，这在一定程度上限制了它们的自主性。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">另外，还有一些工具，如Vercel的v0、Tempo Labs的Tempo和CerebrasCoder，能够帮助用户创建网站，但通常专注于软件技术栈中的某一部分，例如前端开发。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"483\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1056\" data-imgfileid=\"505076557\" data-ratio=\"0.8601851851851852\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bf09dffa-e3d2-46e5-bd5d-7e890015d800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1228\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bf09dffa-e3d2-46e5-bd5d-7e890015d800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">项目级自动化（L3）产品</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">L4：AI软件工程师</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一级别的工具，如Devin、Marblism和Cosine的Genie等，旨在访问终端和部署工具，管理整个开发活动的流程。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"326\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1128\" data-imgfileid=\"505076560\" data-ratio=\"0.5796296296296296\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3543efec-ce28-439e-fd20-f8a977733500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1947\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3543efec-ce28-439e-fd20-f8a977733500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">用Marblism制作的示例项目</span></p>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"301\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1069\" data-imgfileid=\"505076561\" data-ratio=\"0.5351851851851852\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/14a6365a-3e91-4a7b-1e75-36165123f500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1997\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/14a6365a-3e91-4a7b-1e75-36165123f500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">SWE-bench 验证排行榜（截至2024年12月19日）</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些先进的系统不仅能够解读产品需求、管理代码部署，还能维护生产环境中的软件，充分体现了AI软件工程师的角色。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它们的出现，能让非技术人员在短短几分钟内，就能从零开始创建一个功能完整的软件产品，大大降低了软件开发的门槛。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"371\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"873\" data-imgfileid=\"505076563\" data-ratio=\"0.6601851851851852\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e4e39501-dbe2-4b4b-9883-6db6ee2ae600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1323\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e4e39501-dbe2-4b4b-9883-6db6ee2ae600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">AI软件工程师（L4）产品</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">L5：AI开发团队</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在L5级别，AI编程进入了一个全新的领域，可能涉及一个包含多个AI软件工程师的AI系统。这些 AI 代理能够协作完成项目，各自专注于软件开发的不同方面。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">微软的论文《AutoDev》提出，智能体能够从智能体调度器（Agent Scheduleer）接收目标和对话历史，并根据规则和动作配置做出响应。不过，该论文目前仅使用单个GPT-4智能体来进行评估。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"248\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"868\" data-imgfileid=\"505076564\" data-ratio=\"0.44166666666666665\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b18b7d3-ecc2-47e5-cf73-6522bddfae00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1964\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b18b7d3-ecc2-47e5-cf73-6522bddfae00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">参考资料：https://arxiv.org/html/2403.08299v1</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一类别中的另一个产品是MGX，由MetaGPT团队设计，目前处于等待名单阶段。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"329\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1184\" data-imgfileid=\"505076567\" data-ratio=\"0.5851851851851851\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0b96ebb6-0bb6-4254-84c3-83671fa8bf00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2024\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0b96ebb6-0bb6-4254-84c3-83671fa8bf00/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">随着GPT-5预计在2025年发布，AI开发团队的梦想正逐渐从蓝图走向现实。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们可以预见，在不久的将来，AI系统能够复制整个软件开发团队，在软件创作的各个方面进行编程和协作，真正实现软件开发的高度自动化。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"268\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"805\" data-imgfileid=\"505076566\" data-ratio=\"0.47685185185185186\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5ce48686-7c73-4637-d5ac-cc5f873acf00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1689\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5ce48686-7c73-4637-d5ac-cc5f873acf00/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"459\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"920\" data-imgfileid=\"505076565\" data-ratio=\"0.8166666666666667\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f0128441-d567-4a7d-83c1-44bf58a45a00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1126\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f0128441-d567-4a7d-83c1-44bf58a45a00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">AI开发团队（L5）产品</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>如何选择适合的AI编程工具？</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">面对如此丰富多样的AI编程工具，开发者应如何选择呢？这需要依据自身的需求和项目的复杂程度来决定。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果仅仅是需要代码补全功能，那么L1级别的工具，如GitHub Copilot，就能够满足需求。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于更复杂的任务，如功能开发和漏洞修复，可以使用L2级别的LLM，如ChatGPT或Claude 3，并结合工作流自动化工具，如aider或16x Prompt。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">倘若你勇于尝试新事物，对项目级自动化感兴趣，那么L3级别的工具，如Codegen或Sweep，将是一个不错的起点。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">开发者不必局限于使用单个级别的工具，完全可以根据实际需求，组合使用不同级别的工具。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">例如，在遇到简单的代码补全任务，能够在5秒钟内解决的，可使用GitHub Copilot；而对于那些需要花费几分钟来精心设计提示的复杂任务，则可以借助ChatGPT和16x Prompt来处理。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI在编程领域所扮演的角色，正经历着快速的演变。从最初仅能为开发者提供基本语法层面的辅助，到如今已深度渗透至软件开发生命周期的每一个环节，实现全流程的管理与赋能。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">随着AI技术的不断成熟，未来将会涌现出更加复杂、强大的工具，它们将彻底重塑编程领域，让开发者能够专注于高层次的任务，而将软件开发的常规工作交由AI来处理。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从代码补全到全方位开发支持，AI正在重新定义软件开发的未来。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\">参考资料：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\">https://prompt.16x.engineer/blog/ai-coding-l1-l5</span></section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "文章详细解析了 AI 编程工具从 L1 到 L5 的分级体系，涵盖代码补全、任务自动化、项目自动化、AI 软件工程师和多 AI 协作开发团队五个阶段，并探讨了如何根据需求选择工具及未来发展方向。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章详细解析了 AI 编程工具从 L1 到 L5 的分级体系，涵盖代码补全、任务自动化、项目自动化、AI 软件工程师和多 AI 协作开发团队五个阶段，并探讨了如何根据需求选择工具及未来发展方向。",
  "summary": "文章系统性地介绍了 AI 编程工具的五个等级（L1-L5），并对其功能特点、应用场景及技术成熟度进行了深入分析。L1 级别以 GitHub Copilot 为代表，主要聚焦于代码补全；L2 级别如 ChatGPT，专注于任务级自动化，包括功能开发和代码修复；L3 级别如 Codegen，实现了项目级自动化的初步能力，但需要人工干预以确保质量；L4 级别如 Devin，则能管理整个开发流程，体现 AI 软件工程师的角色，大幅降低非技术人员参与软件开发的门槛；L5 级别展望了多 AI 协作的开发团队模式，能够复制整个软件开发团队，在软件创作的各个方面进行编程和协作。文章还探讨了如何根据开发者需求选择合适的工具，并预测了 AI 在编程领域的未来发展趋势，例如 GPT-5 和 AutoDev 等具体技术进展，强调其将重塑软件开发的全流程。",
